    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1922-12-16T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1922-12-16T00:00:00-05:00" n="606"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d606">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">493.11/873</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Comptroller General</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">McCarl</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1922-12-16">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 16, 1922</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: You are informed that in a statement of the
                    accounts of the Chinese Government on account of Chinese Indemnity, Certificate
                    No. 30613 Diplomatic Fiscal Officers, there was found due to the United States
                    as of January 1, 1923, as follows: <table cols="3" rows="4">
                        <row>
                            <cell rendition="#top" role="num">1.</cell>
                            <cell>Part of December 1917, monthly installments, payment
                                deferred,</cell>
                            <cell rendition="#bottom" role="num">$42,822.16</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell rendition="#top" role="num">2.</cell>
                            <cell>Annual installments of $539,588.76 for 1918, 1919, 1920, 1921,
                                1922, payable semi annually, payments deferred,</cell>
                            <cell rendition="#bottom" role="num">2,697,943.80</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell rendition="#top" role="num">3.</cell>
                            <cell>Accrued interest at 4% on amount of deferred payments remaining
                                due and unpaid as of Dec. 31, 1922,</cell>
                            <cell rendition="#bottom #border-bottom" role="num">251,302.74</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell/>
                            <cell/>
                            <cell role="num">2,922,068.70<note n="88" xml:id="d606fn88">Figures as
                                    on original document.</note>
                            </cell>
                        </row>
                    </table>
                </p>
                <p>Respectfully,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">J. R. McCarl</hi>,</signed>
                    <lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Comptroller General</hi>
                    <lb/>
                    <signed>By <hi rend="smallcaps">W. S. Dewhirst</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
